Lingua/FeatureMatrix version 0.01
=================================

This is a module for quickly writing linguistically interesting
featureset notations to describe emes (e.g., phonemes, graphemes).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

HELPER MODULES

Lingua/FeatureMatrix/Eme.pm
which should be part of this distribution. See the MANIFEST.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Class::MethodMaker

